---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-blue max-w-none">
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
        Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how Project Tech collects, uses, and safeguards your information.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800">1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700">
        <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email, phone number, and details you provide during registration.</li>
        <li><strong>Technical Information:</strong> IP address, browser type, and activity collected during your visit.</li>
        <li><strong>Feedback:</strong> Testimonials and reviews you share with us.</li>
      </ul>
      <br>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        We use your information to:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700">
        <li>Deliver and enhance our programs.</li>
        <li>Respond to inquiries and offer support.</li>
        <li>Measure program effectiveness and user satisfaction.</li>
        <li>Provide updates on upcoming workshops and opportunities.</li>
      </ul>
      <br>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800">3. Data Protection</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        We implement appropriate security measures to protect your information. However, no system can guarantee 100% security.
      </p>
      <br>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800">4. Sharing of Information</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700">
        <li>We do not sell your information.</li>
        <li>We may share it with trusted service providers or as required by law.</li>
      </ul>
      <br>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800">5. Your Rights</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        You can request access to, correction, or deletion of your personal information at any time by contacting us at 
        <a href="mailto:contact@project-tech.org" class="text-primary hover:underline">contact@project-tech.org</a>.
      </p>
      <br>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800">6. Cookies</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        Our website uses cookies to enhance your experience. You can disable cookies in your browser settings.
      </p>
      <br>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800">7. Updates</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        We may update this Privacy Policy. Please check back regularly for updates.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
